 VTuber Pekora Usada 合作商品《Pekora》遭诽谤，发布者与卖家达成和解。 https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-slanderous-comments-on-the-collaborative-product-pecola-settlement-reached- Between-contributors-and-distributor/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-slanderous-comments-on-the-collaborative-product-pecola-settlement-reached- Between-contributors-and-distributor/#respondp2y_admin Tue, 26 Sep 2023 08:26:54 +0000 VTuberバーチャルYouTuberコラボレーションバーチャルYouTuberホロライブホロライブプロダクション兎田ぺこら名誉毀損株式会社イクリエ法的措置誹謗中傷 https://p2y.jp/?p=102077 <p> 2023年9月26日（令和5年），Ikurie Co., Ltd.宣布，该公司销售的与VTuber Pekora Usada（隶属于Hololive）的合作产品“Pekora”“含有毒品”。 &#39;</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-slanderous-comments-on-the-collaborative-product-pecola-settlement-reached-between-contributors-and-distributor/">VTuber Pekora Usada 合作商品“Pekora”被诽谤，发帖者与卖家达成和解。</a>首发于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; <p></p><p> 2023 年 9 月 26 日，Ikurie Co., Ltd. 宣布，该公司销售的与 VTuber <strong>Pekora</strong> Usada（隶属于 Hololive）的合作产品“ <strong>Pekora</strong> ”“含有毒品”。宣布已达成和解与多个发布恶意诽谤的人取得联系。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="102084" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-slanderous-comments-on-the-collaborative-product-pecola-settlement-reached-between-contributors-and-distributor/pecola_image/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pecola_image.jpg" data-orig-size="1097,617" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="pecola_image" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pecola_image.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pecola_image.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1097" height="617" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pecola_image.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-102084"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p> “Pekola”是三重县名张市的天然糖浆工厂“U Products”在 Pekora Usada 的监督下生产的精酿可乐糖浆，从 8 月 7 日开始预购。</p><p>对于这款产品，推特（X）上的一些发帖者误认为这是普通可乐而不是稀释可乐糖浆，并抱怨价格高，并问道：“<em>它甚至含有硬币吗？</em> ”经证实，他制作了这款产品。一篇恶意帖子<em>，上面写着“你在放入硬币吗？</em> <em>”并补充道，“我是合作伙伴的员工。实际上，我正在放入硬币。如果我们不这样做，ho↑b ↓直播。”经证实，有人发布恶意恶作剧，自称是制造商/销售商的员工，称“我被高管严厉批评了”。</em></p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image"> <a href="https://twitter.com/yuyu1262eva/status/1691371881323171841" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img data-attachment-id="98938" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usada-pekora-collaboration-product-pecola-seller-considers-legal-action-against-malicious-hoax-contributors-with-drug-include/vtuber_usada_pekora_collaboration_product_pecola_seller_considers_legal_action_against_malicious_hoax_contributors_with_drug_include/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/vtuber_usada_pekora_collaboration_product_pecola_seller_considers_legal_action_against_malicious_hoax_contributors_with_drug_include.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_usada_pekora_collaboration_product_pecola_seller_considers_legal_action_against_malicious_hoax_contributors_with_drug_include" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/upload